		},
		{
			"type": "crafting",
			"recipe": "assemblylinemachines:crafting/tools/mystium/mystium_axe",
			"text": "斧的$(3)额外技能$()是直接砍伐一整棵树的树干，能够更快地砍伐森林。"
		},
