			"text": "锄的$(3)额外技能$()是制造$(item)秘稀耕地$()，一种类似于耕地的方块，但是能够加速植物生长并且永远不会缺水！"
		},
		{
			"type": "text",
			"text": "此外也有秘稀装备可供选择。这套出色的标准装备能使用内部电力吸收物理伤害。此外，大多数部位并没有特殊技能。"
		},
		{
			"type": "crafting",
			"recipe": "assemblylinemachines:crafting/tools/mystium/mystium_leggings",
			"recipe2": "assemblylinemachines:crafting/tools/mystium/mystium_boots"
		},
		{
			"type": "spotlight",
			"item": "assemblylinemachines:mystium_crystal",
			"link_recipe": true,
			"text": "$(5)秘稀水晶$()通过将绿宝石粉和秘稀混合物在搅拌器中与熔岩混合获得。"
		},
		{
			"type": "crafting",
			"recipe": "assemblylinemachines:crafting/tools/mystium/mystium_helmet",
			"recipe2": "assemblylinemachines:crafting/tools/mystium/mystium_chestplate"
